Judul: BRAND AND DISTRIBUTION CHANNEL AS IMPORTANT FACTORS IN DEVELOPING A NEW BUSINESS BRAND
Abstrak: In this final project, the author uses historical data, interviews with relevant parties, and several theories. This research objective is to improve For Our Indonesia performance in clothing business in creative industry. From the analysis, brand and marketing have the most important things in starting business. Especially, the right marketing strategy can create a new brand image in the market.
Kata Kunci: clothing, retail business, brand management, marketing strategy
